  "excerpt": "<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/index.php%3Ftitle%3DEliezer_Yudkowsky%26action%3Dedit%26redlink%3D1\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Eliezer Yudkowsky</a> 在 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/index.php%3Ftitle%3DLessWrong%26action%3Dedit%26redlink%3D1\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">LessWrong</a> 连载的「序列」与 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/Andy_Matuschak\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Andy Matuschak</a> 的<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/index.php%3Ftitle%3DEvergreen_notes%26action%3Dedit%26redlink%3D1\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">常青笔记</a>[1]有诸多相似之处。 他们试图给概念贴上标签，并不害怕创造新的术语，以便使后续的思考更加清晰 他们将原子化的洞见打包成笔记或博客文章，以便在作品的其他地方引用。 他们广…",
